Document: Rendering Renderers
Path: godot/tutorials/rendering/renderers.rst
Summary: This section describes shader features and their compatibility across different renderers.

Shader features
See doc_shading_reference for more information.

*   Screen texture: Supported in Compatibility, Mobile, and Forward+ renderers.
*   Depth texture: Supported in Compatibility, Mobile, and Forward+ renderers.
*   Normal/Roughness buffer: Not supported in Compatibility and Mobile renderers, but supported in Forward+.
*   Compute shaders: Not supported in Compatibility. Supported in Mobile, but comes with a performance penalty on older devices. Supported in Forward+.
